title: Autobots; Roll Out
name: 汽车人，出发
desc: Autobots; Roll Out!\nThe Transformers landed on Top War on August 10; 2021! Will they come back again?

title: Stay Sharp
name: 藏剑于鞘
desc: Stay Sharp\nThe Black Widow trained at the hidden site for 6;935 days.

title: New Element?
name: 新元素？
desc: The New Element?\nLaTest news: Doctor Reichstein discovered the element No. 116

title: Grateful to You
name: 感恩有你
desc: Grateful To You\nWe're thankful to you and the many more memories we will continue to create.

title: Eternal King
name: 永恒之王
desc: Eternal King\nThe first Eternal Land event took place in June 2020; marking the beginning of the epic war

title: One-on-one War
name: 最强之战
desc: One-on-one War\nThe first SVS was launched in May 2019.

title: The Top War
name: 群雄争霸
desc: The Top War\n73.38 million new commanders have joined us this year; ready to fight by your side!

title: The World's Richest
name: 最壕指挥官
desc: The World's Richest\nThe current fortune of the Richest Commander is estimated at $105 trillion according to the TW Billionaires Index.

title: SaND Festival Dishes
name: 沙岛节日料理
desc: SaND Festival Dishes\nUnique dishes for SaND festivals

title: MRE Combat Ration
name: 作战料理包
desc: MRE Combat Ration\nService members take these Meals Ready-to-Eat for use in combat.

title: Dark Legion Ration
name: 黑暗军团料理
desc: Dark Legion Ration\nYou got to admit; this is good.

title: Staff Dinner
name: 员工晚餐
desc: Staff Dinner\nA decent dinner for Zizak Metal Co. Ltd. employees...What's making me eat so much?

title: Freedom League Turkey
name: 自由联盟烤火鸡
desc: Freedom League Turkey\nThe main course during the Thanksgiving feast.

title: Eco-friendly Fireworks
name: 环保烟花
desc: Eco-friendly Fireworks\nNot a true Firework; but it is environmentally friendly.

title: Sparklers
name: 迷你烟花
desc: Sparklers\nWow; such a tiny Fireworks show. Add some more ingredients to the mix.

title: Common Fireworks
name: 家常烟花
desc: Common Fireworks\nIt's just about right; let's make another one.

title: The Willow
name: 纯彩烟花
desc: The Willow\nIt's larger than the Common Fireworks; but it only comes in one color.

title: Comet
name: 神奇烟花
desc: Comet\nNo sound; just a breathtakingly bright light. Try another one; will you?

title: Fountains
name: 超级烟花
desc: Fountains\nThat's huge; and maybe the largest firework set off in Top War.

title: Thunder-bomb Fireworks
name: 双声烟花
desc: Thunder-bomb Fireworks\nOuch; my ears. Is that you; Sir Tinnitus?

title: Chinese Firecrackers
name: 春节烟花
desc: Chinese Firecrackers\nThe Lunar New Year is on 02/01/2022. Happy Lunar New Year; commanders!!

title: Crossette
name: 入世烟花
desc: Crossette\nCrossette; just as lovely as Mei; a star rising from the east; was introduced on 01/06/2022

title: Ground Spinners
name: 穿越的烟花
desc: Ground Spinners\nSpinning and jumping around the way to the Lunar New Year!

title: Skyrocket
name: 英雄烟花
desc: Skyrocket\nA total of 19 new heroes have joined the battle against the Dark Legion in Top War throughout the last year.

title: Flying Fish
name: 城市烟花
desc: Flying Fish\nThe "Ark" is the most popular base skin among commanders; and the Freedom League has created 18 base skins in the last year.

title: Ancient Firecrackers
name: 远古爆竹
desc: Ancient Firecrackers\nMany historians believe that fireworks were first developed in ancient China in 645AD.

title: Fitness Fireworks
name: 健身烟花
desc: Fitness Fireworks\nBen performs 500 push-ups; 500 squats; 500 sit-ups; and a 50-kilometer run every day. As far as we know; Ben is the first and only person to ever beat this record.

title: Glory Fireworks
name: 荣耀烟花
desc: Glory Fireworks\nThe first Top-star Championship was ended on 01/23/2022! This is a moment to celebrate for all commanders!

title: Girandola
name: 彩虹烟花
desc: Girandola\nThe brilliant lights from the blooming fireworks illuminate the night.

title: Anonymous Fireworks
name: 无名烟花
desc: Anonymous Fireworks\nWe don't know much about the mysterious 914. According to some; the Freedom League supports him; but others believe he's a spy.

title: Best Wishes Fireworks
name: 恭喜发财烟花
desc: Best Wishes Fireworks\nWe wish the best of health and success for you and your family in the next year.

title: Beast Fireworks
name: 猛兽烟花
desc: Beast Fireworks\nRambo's team was able to scatter behind the enemy; destroying many 88mm Forts and rescue fellow forces.

title: Novelty Fireworks
name: 锦标赛烟花
desc: Novelty Fireworks\nOn March 16; 1926; Robert Goddard successfully launched the first liquid-fueled rocket in Auburn; Mass.

title: Treasure Fireworks
name: 宝藏烟花
desc: Treasure Fireworks\nIn the last year; Amalia has visited a number of historical sites and has finally discovered nine hidden treasures. Experts of the alliance have never been able to figure out how the painted pattern works.

title: Roman Candles
name: 最强烟花
desc: Roman Candles\nSilence has already taken down 482 prey; no one was able to get away.

title: Chrysanthemum
name: 三色烟花
desc: Chrysanthemum\nFun fact: The primary colors are red; blue; and yellow; while computers use R (R: 255 G: 0 B: 0) G (R: 0 G: 255 B: 0) B (R: 0 G: 0 B: 255) because their screens emit light.

title: Unique Fireworks
name: 识别码烟花
desc: Unique Fireworks\n"Unique ID" is a 12-digit sequence that is exclusive to each commander. Commander; we're delighted to have you here!

title: Mechanical Fireworks
name: 机械烟花
desc: Mechanical Fireworks\nOptimus Prime has a hunch that an evil force is making its way toward Top War from someplace in the cosmos. It's about time.

title: Odinium Fireworks
name: 放射性烟花
desc: Odinium Fireworks\nDue to the high radioactivity; no more than 271 Thor elements may be collected at a time in the Dimensional Mine. Old Delhuyar was severely damaged when she was exposed to an excessive amount of Odinium.

title: Shining Fireworks
name: 砰砰烟花
desc: Shining Fireworks\nA Shining Chest can carry up to 737dd gold coins. According to Dr. Reichstein; "We're still trying to increase the capacity of the chest; but to be honest; I don't have any ideas."

title: Old Times Fireworks
name: 超古代烟花
desc: Old Times Fireworks\nIt's amazing how much energy it takes to maintain these weapons from the old times. These troops are very strong and essential in the battlefield.

title: SaND Fireworks
name: 沙岛烟花
desc: SaND Fireworks\nThere is a deeper meaning to the "SaND" fireworks than just entertaining the crowds. Approximately 181 agents have gone missing. Even if their identities remain a mystery; at the very least; they will not be forgotten.
